org.springframework.web.socket.sockjs.transport

接口 SockJsSessionFactory

  • 所有已知实现类:
    AbstractHttpSendingTransportHandler, EventSourceTransportHandler, HtmlFileTransportHandler, WebSocketTransportHandler, XhrPollingTransportHandler, XhrStreamingTransportHandler

    public interface SockJsSessionFactory
    A factory for creating a SockJS session. TransportHandlers typically also serve as SockJS session factories.
    从以下版本开始:
    4.0
    作者:
    Rossen Stoyanchev

    • 方法概要

      所有方法 实例方法 抽象方法

      Create a new SockJS session.

    • 方法详细资料

      • createSession

        SockJsSession createSession(java.lang.String sessionId,
                            WebSocketHandler handler,
                            java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object> attributes)
        Create a new SockJS session.
        参数:
        sessionId - the ID of the session
        handler - the underlying WebSocketHandler
        attributes - handshake request specific attributes
        返回:
        a new session, never null
